<HEADLINE>
<P>
U.S. SOLDIER KILLS GI 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
GRAFENWOEHR, Germany 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An American soldier opened fire with an automatic rifle in a military dining 
hall, shooting and killing one soldier, wounding another, then seriously 
wounding himself, officials said Wednesday. The names of all three American 
soldiers were withheld pending notification of relatives. 
</P>
</TEXT>
