<DOCNO> LA101190-0063 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 290593 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 11, 1990, Thursday, South Bay Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 5 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
