DEFICIT; UNITED STATES -- POLITICS; CAPITAL GAINS TAX -- UNITED STATES; UNITED 
STATES -- FINANCES; REPUBLICAN PARTY; DEMOCRATIC PARTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
