<P>
49ERS BASKETBALL TEAM TO PRACTICE AT MIDNIGHT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Cal State Long Beach men's basketball team will open practice under new 
Coach Seth Greenberg at midnight Sunday in the university gym. Monday is the 
first day the NCAA permits teams to practice. 
</P>
<P>
