(DEVELOPMENT); IRVINE CO; LAGUNA BEACH (CA) -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; 
GROWTH MANAGEMENT; BONDS; PARKS -- ORANGE COUNTY; LAND USE; PROPERTY SALES; 
