<TEXT>
<P>
Innocent Pleas: Three men indicted last month for allegedly embezzling $1.2 
million from Irvine-based Sterling Savings &amp; Loan pleaded not guilty this 
week. Darrell Dean Knox, 46, of Fallbrook; Richard Russell Holtby, 44, of 
Murietta and Allen Zane Frazier, 38, of Midland, Tex., are scheduled to go to 
trial Nov. 20 in U.S. District Court in Santa Ana. A fourth man -- Daniel Lewis 
O'Brien, 39, of Fontana -- was indicted last month but authorities say he is 
still at large. 
